title: Ballroom Orchestra - 24 Best of Ballroom Dancing Vol 2 (Big Papi
description:
Source: CD + Fresh Cover Art Scan

It really chaps Big Papi's ass to hand cut mp3 tags and scan a cover for this lol  But....what the heck.  It is ballroom music played on what seems to be a Casio keyboard and Big Papi almost tossed this in the trash but figured, hey, maybe this is good enough for dance class.  No frills but it does have the right beats for those dance moves.

If you actually download this please leave a comment.  Big Papi is curious of why you grabbed this.

Oh, there are 4 tracks and within each track are 6 songs for each ballroom genre.  See stats below for track duration.
